Looking to do a little angling?
Look no further than Lake Okeechobee (only 10 minutes away) with its diverse aquaculture. Lake Okeechobee is full of many freshewater species including bass, catfish, bluegills- you name it.
Check out some of these

Okeechobee Airboat Rides and Eco Tours
Ready to fly without leaving the water? Curious about what really goes on in that "river of grass"? Okeechobee Airboat Rides and Eco Tours is the perfect blend of adrenalin and education. Take time to see the Florida wildlife from a view many talk about but very few get to experience.
Book your tour today.
Wagon Wheel Horse Farm
Offering guided trail rides on horses for a unique chance to see Florida in a different way -- the true Florida! You’ll love getting to know our welcoming and knowledgeable guides and the majestic horses as you explore the scenic land. All along the way, you’ll feel like family, even if it’s your first time joining us.
More info
Christ Fellowship
Christ Fellowship Church in Okeechobee is a church that helps you thrive in every area of your life. Our passion is to help you know God and grow with others so that you can discover your purpose and impact the world.
